channel.title: The End Of Journey Two-Tropical Original
channel.description:
Well... I have made my new album. It should be up in a bit. Time to move on to my new album, Futurebass is next!
This will be the last track you hear for awhile. I will be gone for a bit to get some new stuff setup and learn how to make some better content. Anyways enjoy!
SoundCloud: [The End Of Journey Two](https://soundcloud.com/tropical_madman/the-end-of-journey-two)
Hopefully I come back with better skill. Make sure to check out my other albums.
